XirtCMS v1.6 - README
==================================================================================
XirtCMS is an open source content managent sytem that has been developed to create
online websites and applications with ease. The aim of XirtCMS is to provide the 
community with a flexible Content Management System featuring up-to-date 
technologies.

Name      : XirtCMS
Version   : 1.6RC1
Release   : Q1 2012
Author    : A.G. Gideonse
